period and alleviation and dialogue would reign so that all
Angolans would work for the realization of national unity and
reconciliation.
</P>
<P>
Lamego arrived here Thursday to get acquainted with the peace
process in a bid to get to know the attitude of the two sides so
as to promote the peace process. Portuguese is one of the
monitoring countries for the process. 
