<HEADLINE> Ugandan President Meets Burundian Leader </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KAMPALA, September 12 (Xinhua) -- Ugandan President Yoweri
Museveni held talks with visiting Burundian President Pierre
Buyoya on the situation in Burundi at his home village Rwakitura,
