Museveni was mandated by a regional summit on Burundi held in
Dar es Salaam from September 3 to 4 to convey to the government
of Burundi the spirit and content of the summit which pledged to
uphold sanctions against Burundi.
</P>
<P>
The summit also set up a secretariat to monitor compliance by
all participating countries.
</P>
<P>
During the meeting, Museveni briefed Buyoya the summit meeting
deliberation and decisions.
</P>
<P>
Buyoya reiterated his government's commitment to the
negotiations that will result in democratic system in which all
political groups share power and feel securer.
</P>
<P>
He assured Museveni that now the full message on regional
summit has fully communicated and his government will discuss the
proposals of the summit and make every effort to ensure that the
negotiations will take place. 
</P>
</TEXT>
