<HEADLINE> Iran Calls for Efforts to Settle Afghan Crisis </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, September 13 (Xinhua) -- Iranian Foreign Minister Kamal
Kharrazi today called on neighboring countries to exchange views
and continue efforts to put an end to the bloodshed in Afghanistan.
</P>
<P>
