<HEADLINE> Liu Huaqing on Party's Absolute Leadership Over Army </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 13 (Xinhua) -- "Ours is an armed force
under the absolute leadership of the Party," Liu Huaqing said
here today.
</P>
<P>
"All officers and men must conscientiously safeguard the great
banner of Deng Xiaoping Theory, implement to the letter the
Party's line, principles and policies and stick to Party's basic
line for the primary stage of socialism for a hundred years," the
military leader said in a panel discussion attended by delegates
from the People's Liberation Army to the current Party congress.
</P>
<P>
Party's absolute leadership over the army is a fundamental
principle in army building, which should be adhered at any
time, he added.
</P>
<P>
"The Party Central Committee with Jiang Zemin as the core is a
staunch and mature leading collective. We should bear in mind the
entrust of Deng Xiaoping and safeguard the authoritativeness of
this leading collective," he said.
</P>
<P>
"We should conscientiously keep identical with the Party
Central Committee ideologically, politically and in actions, obey
the Party Central Committee and the Central Military Commission
to successfully fulfill the tasks entrusted on us by the Party and
the people and provide a guarantee for the reforms, opening-up and
modernization drive in China," he said.
</P>
<P>
Jiang's report at the opening session of the 15th National
Party Congress is a programmatic document guiding the whole Party,
the whole army and people across China to march under the correct
line set at the Third Plenum of the 11th Party Central Committee,
Liu said.
</P>
<P>
"The great banner of Deng Xiaoping is the one for the whole
party, the whole people and also for the whole army," he said.
</P>
<P>
The most important thing to do in advancing socialism
with Chinese characteristics and the modernization of the
Chinese army is to unswervingly hold high the banner of Deng
Xiaoping Theory, he said.
</P>
<P>
He also call for carrying the fine tradition of the army.
"This is a major issue of fundamental importance in the new
historical period," he stressed.
</P>
<P>
In doing so, he said, it is imperative to adhere to the
principle of placing the army under the absolute leadership of
the Party, persist in serving the people heart and soul, maintain
the revolutionary ideal, spirit and discipline, keep to principle
of seeking truth from facts and the style of hard work,
guard against the influence of money warship, hedonism,
individualism and decadent ideology and culture. 
</P>
</TEXT>
