<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Diary of Party Congress Delegates (Sept. 13) - 2 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The report demands that the Chinese people fully assess the
influence future science and technology, hi-technology in
particular, will exert on the national strength, the social and
economic structure and people's living standards.
</P>
<P>
The report also demands that accelerating scientific and
technological progress should enjoy an essential status in the
economic and social development, so as to make the progress in
science and technology and improvement in laborers' qualities the
real impetus to economic development.
</P>
<P>
The way the report analyzes things from strategic points of
view is an expression of broad vision and far-sightedness.
</P>
<P>
Writing this into the report to the congress is of great
significance for the country's cross-century development.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, I think that the report has set new requirements for
the intellectuals. The report demands intellectuals study more to
become disseminators of advanced thoughts, pioneers of science and
technology, and producers of fine cultural works.
</P>
<P>
The report is an encouragement for the people from the circle
of science and technology, the circle of culture and education,
and other intellectuals. It will inspire us to work energetically
for creations and inventions, and become cultural forces that will
shoulder the historic responsibilities for the country and the
nation.
</P>
<P>
After the congress, the Chinese Academy of Sciences will
reassess its role in the scientific progress of the mankind and
development of the country. The CAS will do what ordinary
universities and enterprises are incapable of accomplishing.
</P>
<P>
We shall inherit historical traditions, get rid of the
drawbacks left over by the planned economy, and search for new
modes that could keep abreast of the times. We shall combine our
advantages in personnel and science and technology with the needs
of the society, and develop national hi-tech industries through
speeding up basic research as well as hi-tech innovations.
</P>
<P>
Continuing to organize its main forces to contribute to key
economic progresses and keep a capable force to achieve
breakthroughs, the CAS will also provide the nation with
consultations for top-level decisions.
</P>
<P>
Besides, the CAS will spread scientific knowledge to the people
in the society and advocate scientific spirits and ethics.
</P>
<P>
As a scientist and a teacher with many years of experience, I
feel excited over the prospect of China. 
</P>
</TEXT>
