<HEADLINE> Iran Protests Killing by Taliban </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, September 13 (Xinhua) -- Iran today lodged a protest on
killing 70 women and children by the Taliban militia in northern
Afghanistan.
</P>
<P>
