<DATE_TIME> 1997-09-13 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Cuba Holds Exile Group Responsible for Bombing Attacks </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HAVANA, September 12 (Xinhua) -- Cuba said Thursday that a
leading Cuban exile group in the United States was behind the
recent bomb attacks on Havana hotels and restaurants.
</P>
<P>
There were "thousands of examples" in the past linking the
group, the Miami-based Cuban American National Foundation (CANF),
to violent attempts to overthrow Cuban President Fidel Castro and
communist rule in Cuba, Foreign Ministry Spokeswoman Marianela
Ferriol said at a regular Foreign Ministry press briefing.
</P>
<P>
"We have convincing arguments and proof of the participation of
the (Cuban American National) Foundation in plans to try to
overthrow the Cuban Revolution," the spokeswoman said.
</P>
<P>
The CANF has denied the allegations.
</P>
<P>
Hotels and restaurants in Havana were bombed at least eight
times from June to September, killing an Italian businessman on
September 4. The Cuban Interior Ministry released a statement
Wednesday condemning the CANF for the attacks, saying the group
organized and financed the bombings.
</P>
<P>
The statement said a Salvadoran "mercenary," employed by the
CANF, had been arrested and confessed to planting bombs in hotels
and restaurants.
</P>
<P>
The U.S. government has said it would help investigate the case
if Cuba provides detailed evidence for the link between the
Salvadoran and the CANF. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE19970913.0208 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-09-13 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Hu Jintao Calls for Arming Party With Deng Xiaoping Theory </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 13 (Xinhua) -- The 15th National Congress of
the Communist Party of China (CPC) is a meeting of great
significance and far-reaching historical importance in the
development of the Party and the country, said Hu Jintao here
today.
</P>
<P>
Addressing a discussion attended by Tibetan delegates to the
congress this morning, Hu Jintao said the theme of the current
congress is to hold high the great basnner of Deng Xiaoping Theory
for an all-round advancement of the cause of building socialism
with Chinese characteristics to the 21st century. It tallies with
the wishes of the Party and the people and represents the
requirements of the times and the aspirations of the people, he
added.
</P>
<P>
He said he believes that the congress is sure to mobilize and
unite all members of the Party and of all ethnic groups in the
country and march along the road of socialism with Chinese
characteristics charted by Deng Xiaoping.
</P>
<P>
During the discussion, Chen Kuiyuan, secretary of the Tibetan
Automous Regional Committee of the Communist Party of China, and
two other Tibetan delegates highly praised the report given by
Jiang Zemin at the opening session held yesterday.
</P>
<P>
They also reviewed the achievements Tibet scored in the reform
and development over the past five years.
</P>
<P>
They were of the view that Jiang's report covered a wide range
of subjects, talking about problems in an in-depth way and seeking
truth from facts.
</P>
<P>
After hearing their speeches, Hu said, "The five years since
the 14th Party Congress constituted an unusual period in which our
cause advanced."
</P>
<P>
Deng Xiaoping Theory and the basic line guiding the work in the
primary stage of socialism set in accordance with this theory have
been proved to be entirely correct, he said.
</P>
<P>
Practice in the past five years has shown that the Party
Central Committee with Comrade Jiang Zemin at the core has been
persisting in the basic theory and the basic line of building
socialism with Chinese characteristics and is capable of
controlling the overall situation, uniting the people and
advancing the great cause of China. It is a united, staunch and
mature leading body, Hu added.
</P>
<P>
At present, he stated, "we are confronted with rare
opportunities and grave challenges. Various kinds of problems are
unvoidable on our way ahead. We must be sober-minded and
cautious."
</P>
<P>
"On the new long march into the next century, we must hold high
the great banner of Deng Xiaoping Theory and make it a guidance
for our work in all trades," he added.
</P>
<P>
It is necessary to arm the whole Party and all officials and
the people with Deng Xiaoping Theory, he stressed, adding this is
a long-term stratetic task.
</P>
<P>
"We should be fully aware that we are still in the primary
stage of socialism. We should tackle the major problems in this
period, take economic development as the central task and
concentrate on developing the productive forces," he said.
</P>
<P>
In the course of deepening the reform and building a socialist
market economy, it is imperative to emancipate the mind, seek
truth from facts and be bold in exploring new ways, Hu said.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE19970913.0209 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-09-13 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Diary of Party Congress Delegates (Sept. 12) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 13 (Xinhua) -- (At Xinhua's request, some
delegates to the ongoing 15th National Congress of the Chinese
Communist Party (CPC) write what they see, discuss and think
during the congress in the form of diary, which we think will
provide outsiders with some information about this major event.
The following diary, the first of its kind, was written by Li
Zhongjie, professor of the Party School of the CPC Central
Committee -- Editor)
</P>
<P>
The word "banner" always inspires me and I believe that all
those Party members would feel the same way when they gather
under the hammer-and-sickle Party flag.
</P>
<P>
Today, the banner has again become a focus of attention at the
ongoing Party congress. In hotel rooms, or the foyer of the Great
Hall of the People, the delegates would talk about the issue of
banner when they meet each other.
</P>
<P>
I brought several of my book entitled "The Great Banner Across
the Century" here, which was published prior to the congress.
Before long, delegates and reporters who are interested in
the book came to ask for it though I didn't mention it to
anyone. Now, all the books I brought here are gone.
</P>
<P>
In the morning, Jiang Zemin delivered a report to the 2000-plus
delegates to the congress.
</P>
<P>
When Jiang said that "to adhere to Deng Xiaoping Theory means
to adhere genuinely to Marxism-Leninism and Mao Zedong Thought; to
hold high the banner of Deng Xiaoping Theory means to hold high
genuinely the banner of Marxism-Leninism and Mao Zedong Thought,"
all the delegates gave him a warm applause.
</P>
<P>
Why does the issue of banner draw such close attention? The
answer is just as what Jiang said in his report: "The issue of
banner is of the utmost importance. The banner represents our
orientation and image."
</P>
<P>
Following the death of Deng Xiaoping, what kind of banner to be
held and what road to take in China will determine the future and
fate of China in the 21st century, and will have a direct bearing
on the 1.2 billion Chinese people, and will also affect the
overall economic and political situation worldwide. Therefore, all
Party members and all the Chinese people have been paying close
attention to the issue of banner.
</P>
<P>
In a word, the banner represents the orientation and future
of China.
</P>
<P>
After Deng passed away last February, some China experts
overseas had the worry that China would not have a leader and
cohesion and even might be trapped in chaos.
</P>
<P>
At the opening session of the congress, Jiang clearly vowed to
hold high unswervingly the banner of Deng Xiaoping Theory. This
has shown that the CPC is consistent and firm in the fundamental
issue that determines the future and fate of China.
</P>
<P>
Holding high the banner of Deng Xiaoping Theory is the choice
of practice, the choice of the people and choice of history.
</P>
<P>
As a matter of fact, Jiang expounded the issue in a key speech
delivered on May 29 at the Party School of the CPC Central
Committee.
</P>
<P>
I talked about my personal ideas on studying the speech in an
article in the weekly news-magazine "Outlook" as well as in my
book "The Great Banner Across the Century".
</P>
<P>
When I again heard the incisive remarks made by Jiang today, I
was deeply touched.
</P>
<P>
The Deng Xiaoping Theory is a scientific theory that is closely
connected with every Party member and every Chinese citizen.
</P>
<P>
During the new era of socialist reforms and opening-up and
modernization drive, and on the new march into the next century,
we must hold high the banner of Deng Xiaoping Theory, and use the
theory to guide our overall cause and every undetaking.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE19970913.0210 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-09-13 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Czech Newspaper Hails CPC 15th National Congress </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PRAGUE, September 12 (Xinhua) -- A Czech Republic newspaper,
the Economic News, said here today that the 15th National Congress
of the Communist Party of China (CPC) will exert a great influence
on China's development in the next few years.
</P>
<P>
In a signed article, the newspaper said that the world has
closely watched the 15th National Congress of the CPC, which
opened in Beijing on Friday.
</P>
<P>
It said that although the discussion at the congress is more
frank, China's policy will have no fundamental change. The country
will continue to advance along the course charted by the late
leader Deng Xiaoping, it noted.
</P>
<P>
The newspaper stressed that the CPC 15th National Congress will
bring a great change to the field of economy in China. 
</P>
</TEXT>
